  "title": "Hangar Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>In charge of performing cleaning duties both inside and outside the aircraft during maintenance.</li><li>In charge of assisting in moving and positioning aircraft ground support equipment.</li><li>In charge of conducting minor paint touch-ups, including screws and fasteners, using brushes.</li><li>Responsible in following all safety regulations and maintenance protocols to ensure a secure working environment.</li><li>Responsible in maintaining a clean and organized hangar environment.</li><li>Support the maintenance team when required</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min Nitec in Aerospace Engineering or related</li><li>Min 2 year of working experience in Aerospace Base Maintenance</li><li>Scissor and Boom Lift certification will be advantage</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call <strong>+(65) </strong><a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
